{"tid":1401102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普用差別的關稅政策，建立了美洲的經濟同盟。","createTime":"2019-08-03T14:15:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T03:09:32.000Z","uid":107060,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d17955f0f2cb64490850b471081e0414c2400e9c","tid":1401102,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:15:18.000Z","msg":"陳雲：特朗普的Make America Great Again的America，可以是美洲。特朗普用差別的關稅政策，建立了美洲的經濟同盟。<br />\n特朗普向中國徵稅之後，2019年上半年，美國的最大貿易夥伴是墨西哥，跟著是加拿大，中國排第三。中國出口到美國減少12%。美國出口到中國減少19%。（今日《華爾街日報》報導）<br />\n關稅同盟是國際關係及區域政治的犀利手段，是往日北歐眾多城邦的結盟手段。好多人只是看到特朗普在玩徵稅（a Tariff Man），而不知道他在塑造美國接鄰的區域經濟。他在玩美國與墨西哥的圍牆遊戲的時候，同時加強美墨經濟夥伴關係。<br />\n關稅結盟這種古老戰術，在《香港城邦論》有充分的說明，也是華夏經學《春秋》的主題之一。<br />\n美國訂立的《美國-香港政策法1992》（俗稱《香港關係法》），給予香港獨立關稅區的待遇，也是關稅同盟。在訂立此法的1992年，已經啟動香港建國的契機。"},{"pid":"ab14744d6301971daaa27324cbe126d87d66930e","tid":1401102,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:16:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化<br />\n明白大家唔同意見<br />\n呢篇野原意唔係反港獨<br />\n而係希望大家集中翻五大訴求</span></span><br />\n港獨？小心啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400357\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d606f45b5bd3f7ededc110ccb26aeca5cd4d7cac","tid":1401102,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:18:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db1d574c8bcd20c7ea5df41a852198f6c3fc9529","tid":1401102,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:50:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77970f5b93d61c3cbe2aae294d86901030fac338","tid":1401102,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:45:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"406e9caa204cf6f785083f1b1f9960e39c1e3f2c","tid":1401102,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:01:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a7dcabc021845bbd324f1b371dabb40bdb41c1b","tid":1401102,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:09:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}